{% set name = "fooof" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:

  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

    - scipy >=0.19.0

    - numpy
    - python >=3.5
    - scipy >=0.19.0

    - fooof.bands
    - fooof.core

    - fooof.objs

    - fooof.sim
    - fooof.tests
    - fooof.tests.analysis
    - fooof.tests.bands
    - fooof.tests.core
    - fooof.tests.data
    - fooof.tests.objs
    - fooof.tests.plts
    - fooof.tests.sim
    - fooof.tests.utils
    - fooof.utils
  requires:
    - pytest
